Hi! We are Irene, Venny, and Zulva of VIZ Team from Indonesia.

We are participating in the Grand Final of Project Management Challenge (PMC) 2017 which will be held in Yogyakarta from May 19th to 22nd. PMC 2017 aims to raise the awareness about the importance of project management skill among university students as a part of programs conducted by Project Management Institute, Indonesia Chapter.

What is Project Management?
Project management is the application of knowledge, skills, tools, and techniques to project activities to meet project requirement which includes project initiating, planning, executing, monitoring and controlling, and closing.
